WEBVTT

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:01.616
At first my mom and sisters
and I made the mistake

00:01:01.640 --> 00:01:03.720
of putting him in a regular nursing home.

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:05.856
It was really pretty;

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:08.816
it had plush carpet
and afternoon art classes

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:10.640
and a dog named Diane.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:12.880
But then I got a phone call.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:17.640
"Ms. Malone, we've arrested your father."

00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:20.000
"What?"

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:23.760
"Well, he threatened
everybody with cutlery.

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:27.096
And then he yanked
the curtains off the wall,

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:29.440
and then he tried
to throw plants out the window.